  "title": "People & Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle end-to-end HR operations and administration</li><li>Manage full recruitment lifecycle</li><li>Maintain employee records using HR systems (Infotech or similar)</li><li>Coordinate onboarding, offboarding, and employee documentation</li><li>Support HR compliance and basic understanding of Malaysia employment policies</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>3+ years of experience in HR Operations, Admin, and Recruitment</li><li>Hands-on experience with HRMS / HR systems</li><li>Strong knowledge of full employment lifecycle</li><li>Familiarity with Malaysia employment policy is an added advantage</li><li>Strong Communication skills</li></ul><p></p><p></p>",
